Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.67,0:00:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,戌时已到
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.50,0:00:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,犬夜叉马上要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.04,0:00:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,为了找齐四魂之玉碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.81,0:00:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,为了用这把铁碎牙打败奈落
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.20,0:00:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,打败了蛮骨
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.57,0:00:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,跟七人帮的激战\N总算告一个段落的犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.71,0:00:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,得到七人帮的\N四魂之玉碎片的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.05,0:00:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,新生奈落终于现身
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.05,0:00:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,弥勒法师  珊瑚\N七宝跟云母
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.72,0:00:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,穿梭于时空\N发生在战国时代与现代
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.12,0:00:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.02,0:00:25.15,*Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.15,0:00:32.15,OP,,0,0,0,,分散在蓝蓝天空上的 七颗星星
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.05,0:00:36.86,OP,,0,0,0,,每一颗星星 都刻着我的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.17,0:00:40.77,OP,,0,0,0,,就算梦想被粉碎 我也要寻找爱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.07,0:00:44.80,OP,,0,0,0,,我无处可逃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.02,0:00:48.87,OP,,0,0,0,,紧紧抓着我的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.10,0:00:57.30,OP,,0,0,0,,那些骗人的光阴 我再也不会输给它
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.37,0:01:02.67,OP,,0,0,0,,睁大眼睛 看清楚这瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.67,0:01:06.85,OP,,0,0,0,,它仍然紧紧围绕着我们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.12,0:01:10.85,OP,,0,0,0,,让人啜泣的 现实生活中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.85,0:01:14.85,OP,,0,0,0,,最重要的…到底是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.55,0:01:18.72,OP,,0,0,0,,繁忙的这个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.72,0:01:22.95,OP,,0,0,0,,永恒的碎片 忽隐又忽现
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.95,0:01:26.87,OP,,0,0,0,,去触摸 去捕捉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.02,0:01:33.80,OP,,0,0,0,,我们就要循着目标继续向前走
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.97,0:01:39.03,OP,,0,0,0,,为了得到最后的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.03,0:01:46.27,OP,,0,0,0,,我们就要循着目标继续向前走
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.59,0:02:01.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.53,0:02:07.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爆流破
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.50,0:02:45.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你  云母
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.13,0:02:48.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇  我接住你了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.71,0:02:54.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.41,0:02:57.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.88,0:02:58.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.08,0:03:01.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.28,0:03:02.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.55,0:03:06.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.22,0:03:08.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么了  犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.39,0:03:10.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.66,0:03:16.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第123话\N新生的奈落出现于黑暗尽处
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.43,0:03:21.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.24,0:03:24.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.68,0:03:33.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.48,0:03:35.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢天谢地
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.98,0:03:38.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…你这个傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.95,0:03:41.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干嘛跑到\N这么危险的地方来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.72,0:03:42.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.62,0:03:46.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是交代过你\N要你在外面等我的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.93,0:03:56.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人家真的…很担心你嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.81,0:04:01.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干嘛担这个心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.64,0:04:05.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瘦皮狼  你果然没有照顾好…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.58,0:04:09.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瘦皮狼那个笨蛋到哪去啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.58,0:04:14.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钢牙已经被肉墙吸进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.39,0:04:17.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是说瘦皮狼…被吸进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.69,0:04:21.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以说  你最好马上离开这里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.03,0:04:27.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶  什么怪东西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.11,0:04:32.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇  快离开这
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.98,0:04:40.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个声音是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.05,0:04:42.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是奈落
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.35,0:04:47.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的是奈落吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.49,0:04:48.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.99,0:04:51.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可怕的一股妖气
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.29,0:04:53.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一定和奈落有很大关系…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.00,0:04:59.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.44,0:05:03.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,动不了了吧  犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.00,0:05:06.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落  你…你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.33,0:05:28.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你竟然能找到这里来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.46,0:05:31.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本来想赞许你一番的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.27,0:05:33.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惜太迟了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.67,0:05:39.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你马上就要\N变成我奈落的五脏六腑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.91,0:05:41.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来是该结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.78,0:05:44.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么结束  你别作梦了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.78,0:05:46.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要结束是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.75,0:05:49.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也得等我割断你的喉咙再说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.28,0:05:51.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.42,0:05:55.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天我们要定了你的那条命
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.56,0:05:57.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落  受死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.44,0:06:10.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚  小心点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.64,0:06:12.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好烫…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.01,0:06:14.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个是…强酸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.38,0:06:17.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕  开始溶化了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.71,0:06:21.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.15,0:06:26.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.52,0:06:28.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.83,0:06:33.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇  七宝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.97,0:06:39.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一些笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.10,0:06:41.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道还不明白吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.97,0:06:48.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在整座白灵山\N全都是我奈落的身体了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.98,0:06:52.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,换句话说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.61,0:06:56.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们一个个都在我身体里面
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.19,0:07:00.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这座肉墙真的是奈落的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.05,0:07:04.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇  难道我们跟钢牙一样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.19,0:07:06.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就要被奈落吃掉了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.06,0:07:10.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别太高估自己了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.86,0:07:13.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们还没有被吃掉的价值
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.07,0:07:15.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过是没用的小妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.14,0:07:17.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是在说我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.27,0:07:21.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有像犬夜叉这种半妖
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.08,0:07:25.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们几个人类就更别说了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.01,0:07:30.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只会减损我奈落的威力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.59,0:07:34.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蛮骨
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.66,0:07:36.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他已经死了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.66,0:07:43.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们人类的愚蠢\N简直是叫我作呕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.80,0:07:48.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像蛮骨这样的邪魔歪道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.10,0:07:49.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了帮兄弟们报仇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.97,0:07:52.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也敢闯进这个禁地
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.41,0:07:56.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟犬夜叉你搏斗呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.61,0:08:03.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我把七块碎片给了七人帮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.95,0:08:07.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦这些碎片都得手后
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.99,0:08:10.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不管什么报仇不报仇的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.36,0:08:12.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早早逃之夭夭不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.74,0:08:23.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偏偏这小子…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.28,0:08:31.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫做人类的这种生物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.11,0:08:33.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实在是太愚蠢了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.80,0:08:53.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落  你这臭家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.94,0:08:59.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许他真的像你说的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.81,0:09:01.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是邪魔歪道没错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.18,0:09:06.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七人帮所有兄弟们\N一个个都战死了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.15,0:09:08.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天我要替他们讨回公道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.72,0:09:17.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么啦  犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.79,0:09:19.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了让你更容易\N取得四魂之玉碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.69,0:09:22.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我故意用这双手跟你对打呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.83,0:09:25.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过就算如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.83,0:09:29.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他可是比你正直几百倍以上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.10,0:09:32.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风之伤
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.48,0:09:38.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而奈落你居然…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.05,0:09:40.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这可恶至极的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.05,0:09:45.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干嘛发那么大火呢  犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.35,0:09:48.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蛮骨可是先死在你手中的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.89,0:09:50.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少废话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.37,0:10:04.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.61,0:10:19.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不客气的收下了\N这些四魂之玉碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.80,0:10:31.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四魂之玉碎片\N已经合而为一了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.53,0:10:35.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于现身了吗  奈落…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.04,0:10:45.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这股妖气…一定错不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.05,0:10:50.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您在跟我说话吗\N杀生丸少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.55,0:10:57.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落  已经现身了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.63,0:11:03.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除了杀生丸少爷之外
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.53,0:11:06.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么厉害的妖气\N我还是头一次见识到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.33,0:11:09.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再这样跟下去\N说不定我就因此送命了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.27,0:11:11.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀生丸少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.41,0:11:18.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祝你一战成功
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.31,0:11:22.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.68,0:11:23.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.55,0:11:26.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.15,0:11:29.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.09,0:11:32.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  马上就会结束
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.09,0:11:35.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道不用再等了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.80,0:11:39.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神乐  已经离开这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.84,0:11:48.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.61,0:11:57.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四魂之玉碎片全都聚集了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.90,0:13:25.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.54,0:13:28.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是奈落的新生肉体
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.78,0:13:32.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.22,0:13:42.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是可怜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.12,0:13:45.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们这些\N对我恨之入骨的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.13,0:13:47.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,费尽千辛万苦总算找到我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.63,0:13:51.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是现在\N却连我的一根指头都碰不到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.83,0:13:54.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛\N也太让我们扫兴了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.80,0:13:57.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你处心积虑地躲在这圣地里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.74,0:14:00.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还在猜\N你是会变成多厉害的妖怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.71,0:14:04.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你错了  犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.94,0:14:05.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落现在…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.31,0:14:08.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.48,0:14:12.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落的妖气\N不知比以前强多少倍呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.72,0:14:14.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他有妖气
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.82,0:14:15.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要笑死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.99,0:14:19.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.66,0:14:22.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,分明是奈落又在装神弄鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.86,0:14:26.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他那点功力\N只会越变越差而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.14,0:14:36.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.68,0:14:42.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,散魂铁爪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.02,0:14:51.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真爱开玩笑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.89,0:14:55.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然徒手也敢跟我奈落斗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.03,0:14:58.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.03,0:15:00.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然你那么想死的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.27,0:15:01.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本少爷就将你碎尸万段
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.07,0:15:06.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧  铁碎牙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.51,0:15:17.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙  乖乖的受死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.88,0:15:18.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看招
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.89,0:15:21.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风之伤
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.96,0:15:29.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋一个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.34,0:15:38.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.67,0:15:40.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风之伤被打回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.35,0:15:46.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.25,0:15:48.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.59,0:15:54.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风之伤竟然停不下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.69,0:15:55.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.69,0:15:59.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒法师\N快躲到飞来骨后面
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.99,0:16:01.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会这样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.63,0:16:05.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.73,0:16:07.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那个什么风之伤
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.50,0:16:10.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全被我的妖气控制住了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.10,0:16:12.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇  你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.14,0:16:15.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉你这个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.74,0:16:17.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁叫你中了奈落的计
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.74,0:16:19.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发动什么风之伤
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.75,0:16:20.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少罗唆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.95,0:16:22.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.09,0:16:29.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风之伤会在这里不断地徘徊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.99,0:16:32.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直到你们\N全都被打成肉酱为止
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.43,0:16:36.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉  你这小子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.30,0:16:42.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到自己发动的风之伤\N会害死你的伙伴们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.91,0:16:56.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白灵山里面\N到处弥漫着妖气
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.46,0:17:05.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是奈落的分身  神乐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.46,0:17:07.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她怀里抱的是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.61,0:17:22.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好险
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.44,0:17:24.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是桔梗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.48,0:17:26.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别乱来  神乐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.11,0:17:30.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗轮不到你来收拾她
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.39,0:17:34.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来这家伙会说话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.49,0:17:36.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.60,0:17:53.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落\N你到底又放走了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.91,0:17:55.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.22,0:18:06.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇  你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.43,0:18:13.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要让这阵风…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.83,0:18:15.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要想办法\N让这阵风停下来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.63,0:18:21.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉他们马上会死在这了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.40,0:18:25.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而我也已经得到新的肉体
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.74,0:18:29.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只剩下最后一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.65,0:18:35.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落  你想逃走吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.02,0:18:39.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.42,0:18:42.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快追  犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.99,0:18:43.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.26,0:18:45.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快去追奈落
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.03,0:18:49.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了  可是你怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.96,0:18:51.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟你一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.93,0:18:54.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果这阵风\N真的是奈落的妖气
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.00,0:18:56.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定我有办法让它停下来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.94,0:18:59.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更何况  刚刚我看见了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.81,0:19:03.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落的脚底\N有其他两块四魂之玉碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.28,0:19:05.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有两块
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.38,0:19:07.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是瘦皮狼的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.68,0:19:08.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.02,0:19:10.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钢牙他是妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.78,0:19:13.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我担心会被奈落\N化为他身体的一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.69,0:19:16.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们一定要救他
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.46,0:19:19.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这还得看他\N是不是还活着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.85,0:19:49.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全都疯了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.49,0:19:51.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然从风之伤里飞了出来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.83,0:19:55.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.90,0:19:58.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那股妖气是绕着奈落转动的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.87,0:20:00.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别管这些了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.07,0:20:03.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就瞄准奈落这个坏蛋射箭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.74,0:20:04.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.61,0:20:07.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看箭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.89,0:20:27.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,射中了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.64,0:20:40.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钢牙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.45,0:20:48.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个时候\N还有心情关心朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.38,0:20:52.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实在看不下去你们的愚蠢了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.32,0:20:55.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风之伤停下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.66,0:20:57.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.86,0:21:01.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然这么关心朋友的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.60,0:21:10.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞什么鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.50,0:21:11.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,山要崩塌了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.21,0:21:18.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了  是瘴气
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.68,0:21:21.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天就特别开恩
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.72,0:21:25.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你们跟好友们一起长眠
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.68,0:21:59.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.65,0:22:02.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我马上就去见你了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.65,0:23:37.65,ED,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.35,0:22:13.33,ED,,0,0,0,,偷偷亲你一下 装作若无其事的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.33,0:22:18.40,ED,,0,0,0,,我这样调皮 是不是像个孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.68,0:22:24.83,ED,,0,0,0,,早已习惯 被你说是娇嗔无理
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.83,0:22:34.55,ED,,0,0,0,,不过「喜欢你」这三个字却始终说不出口 My Sweet Emotion
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.53,0:22:45.48,ED,,0,0,0,,对着镜子 多看一次 看看自己的微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.25,0:22:58.78,ED,,0,0,0,,如果想飞奔出去追求刺激就得挺起胸膛向前走
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.15,0:23:09.68,ED,,0,0,0,,大胆放手去做 直到满意为止
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.85,0:23:18.73,ED,,0,0,0,,偷偷亲你一下 装作若无其事的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.73,0:23:23.90,ED,,0,0,0,,我这样调皮 是不是像个孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.20,0:23:30.48,ED,,0,0,0,,早已习惯 被你说是娇嗔无理
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.48,0:23:39.95,ED,,0,0,0,,不过「喜欢你」这三个字却始终说不出口 My Sweet Emotion
